		<p>Welcome to the Eagle FLEX web system. This site is designed for you, the coach, to be able to track the wellness of your athletes.
			This will be done through surveys that you can modify and send to your teams.</p>
		<p>The <strong>surveys</strong> page will allow you to edit or send wellness surveys to your athletic teams.</p>
